== 反对意见 ==
兴建该核电站计划引起了社会关注。非政府组织开展了活动反对建设核电站，并收集了反对建造新核电站的签名 <ref name="naviny7">{{Cite news|url=http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/06/13/ic_news_259_292139/|title=Group in Horki, Mahilyow region, said to have collected more than 2,500 signatures against nuclear power plant project|publisher=Belarusian News|date=2008-06-13|accessdate=2008-08-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080615022228/http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/06/13/ic_news_259_292139/|archivedate=2008-06-15|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref name="naviny10">{{Cite news|url=http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/02/21/ic_news_259_286163/|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121203072026/http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/02/21/ic_news_259_286163/|archivedate=2012-12-03|title=Campaigners to collect signatures against construction of nuclear power plant in Cherykaw district|publisher=Belarusian News|date=2008-02-21|accessdate=2008-08-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。{{le|白俄罗斯人民阵线|Belarusian People's Front}}的年轻成员组织了活动反对俄罗斯参与电站建设，并敦促白俄罗斯政府将合同授予俄罗斯之外国家的公司。 <ref name="naviny6">{{Cite news|url=http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/05/11/ic_news_259_290332/|title=Opposition youths to campaign against Russia's involvement in construction of Belarusian nuclear power plant|publisher=Belarusian News|date=2008-05-11|accessdate=2008-08-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080516105504/http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/05/11/ic_news_259_290332/|archivedate=2008-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>除此之外，一群白俄罗斯科学家发起了“白俄罗斯无核化”运动，声称白俄罗斯政府在1999年通过的停核令到期之前就开始筹备建造核电站。该暂停令于2009年1月14日到期<ref name="naviny8">
{{Cite news|url=http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/03/11/ic_media_259_1691/|title=Video: Scientists come out against construction of nuclear power plant in Belarus|publisher=Belarusian News|date=2008-03-11|accessdate=2008-08-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513161612/http://naviny.by/rubrics/inter/2008/03/11/ic_media_259_1691/|archivedate=2008-05-13}}
</ref>。 

邻国立陶宛对建设该电厂持批评态度，并打算抵制该电厂<ref name="delfi">{{Cite web |url=https://en.delfi.lt/central-eastern-europe/lithuania-not-in-talks-with-belarus-on-electricity-from-n-plan.d?id=78985151 |title=Belarus nuclear plant: A disaster waiting to happen |accessdate=2020-12-08 |archive-date=2020-12-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228223501/https://en.delfi.lt/politics/lithuania-not-in-talks-with-belarus-on-electricity-from-n-plan.d?id=78985151 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 核电站的安全问题使其备受关注，该核电站仅在建设过程中就发生了几起严重的事故，而白俄罗斯监管部门在数周后才通报了事件<ref name="delfi" />。

== 事故 ==
2016年7月10日，在一次测试起吊的过程中，重达330吨的[[反應爐壓力槽|反應爐壓力槽]]从二至四米的高度砸到地面<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=Belarus under fire for 'dangerous errors' at nuclear plant|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/09/belarus-under-fire-for-dangerous-errors-at-nuclear-plant|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2016-08-09|accessdate=2020-12-09|issn=0261-3077|language=en-GB|first=Tony|last=Wesolowsky|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228223552/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/aug/09/belarus-under-fire-for-dangerous-errors-at-nuclear-plant|dead-url=no}}</ref>。核电站的建设方{{link-en|俄罗斯原子能公司|Rosatom}}随后在8月2日确认了事故，称工人在起吊时没有正确固定核岛，导致其着地。该公司称事故没有导致任何损失。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Construction Halted on Belarus Nuclear Plant After Workers Drop Reactor Vessel|url=https://www.powermag.com/construction-halted-on-belarus-nuclear-plant-after-workers-drop-reactor-vessel/|accessdate=2020-12-09|date=2016-08-11|last=Overton|first=Thomas|work=POWER Magazine|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228223459/https://www.powermag.com/construction-halted-on-belarus-nuclear-plant-after-workers-drop-reactor-vessel/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年11月10日，该电站在白俄罗斯总统卢卡申科宣布正式启用的三天后就因故停止了发电。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Belarus nuclear plant stops power output soon after opening|url=https://apnews.com/article/ukraine-alexander-lukashenko-belarus-lithuania-b143687f7537ae207c95b5000f9a6b72|accessdate=2020-12-09|author=|date=2020-11-10|format=|work=AP NEWS|publisher=|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228223504/https://apnews.com/article/ukraine-alexander-lukashenko-belarus-lithuania-b143687f7537ae207c95b5000f9a6b72|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="rferl3stopped">{{Cite web|title=Belarusian Nuclear Plant Stops Electricity Output Three Days After Opening Ceremony|url=https://www.rferl.org/a/belarusian-nuclear-plant-stops-electricity-output-days-after-opening-ceremony/30940530.html|accessdate=2020-12-09|work=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228223610/https://www.rferl.org/a/belarusian-nuclear-plant-stops-electricity-output-days-after-opening-ceremony/30940530.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>该设施的几台变压器发生爆炸，导致反应堆暂停向电网输电。 <ref name="rferl3stopped" />维修变压器耗费了九天，反应堆在维护结束后重新联网。<ref>{{Cite news|title=BelNPP reconnected to grid after equipment replacement|url=https://eng.belta.by/economics/view/belnpp-reconnected-to-grid-after-equipment-replacement-135123-2020/|accessdate=2020-11-27|work=Belarusian Telegraph Agency|date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228223558/https://eng.belta.by/economics/view/belnpp-reconnected-to-grid-after-equipment-replacement-135123-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>因对反应堆安全极度不信任，立陶宛政府在2020年10月底开始向其居民发放[[碘化钾|碘片]]，以预防可能发生的[[核事故|核事故]]。截止到2020年11月19日，超过两百万碘片已经被发放到居民的手中<ref>{{Cite web|title=Vilniaus miesto savivaldybė - Distribution of iodine tables has been extended in the capital till 17 December|url=https://vilnius.lt/en/2020/11/19/on-tuesday-the-capital-starts-distributing-iodine-tablets-residents-of-vilnius-will-be-able-to-pick-them-up-at-pharmacies-free-of-charge/|accessdate=2020-12-09|date=2020-11-19|work=Vilniaus miesto savivaldybė|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201228223540/https://vilnius.lt/en/2020/11/19/on-tuesday-the-capital-starts-distributing-iodine-tablets-residents-of-vilnius-will-be-able-to-pick-them-up-at-pharmacies-free-of-charge/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

